  <brief_title>Pilot Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Treatment With ORA102 Combined With Avastin (Bevacizumab) Versus Avastin Alone, in Patients With Neovascular Age Related Macular Degeneration (AMD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Multi-Center, Double Blind, 3 Arm, Phase I/II Pilot Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Treatment With ORA102 Combined With Avastin (Bevacizumab) Versus Avastin Alone, in Patients With Neovascular Age Related Macular Degeneration (AMD)</official_title>
