  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is s randomized, multi-center, double blind, 3 arm, phase I/II pilot study to evaluate
      the safety and efficacy of treatment with ORA102 combined with Avastin (Bevacizumab) versus
      Avastin alone, in patients with neo-vascular age related macular degeneration (AMD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
